title: The Way of Kings - Brandon Sanderson - large images
description:
Epub format, 7.89mb


The images in the epubs I've found of this book are quite low quality.  This version has larger images, which were sourced from the gallery on Brandon's website.

As a bonus, it has an artwork of a Cryptic inserted as well.

If you enjoy this book, consider buying it. I recommend the hardback version to take advantage of these great illustrations.


If you're looking for an android app that will let you zoom in on images in epubs, I recommend Lithium. It is free!
